{"tid":585703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(阿波羅) 習近平江澤民已達成稱帝協議:  不平反六四","createTime":"2018-03-09T01:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T05:02:08.000Z","uid":134071,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"04f01bf4b1d6ca996f2738e57242168ed12645cc","tid":585703,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T01:50:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.aboluowang.com/2018/0303/1078577.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.aboluowang.com%2F2018%2F0303%2F1078577.html&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pvzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=cff4acd7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.aboluowang.com/2018/0303/1078577.html</a><br />\n<br />\n人民報獨家：習近平江澤民已達成協議<br />\n【阿波羅新聞網 2018-03-03 訊】作者：姜平默認<br />\n主要內容如下： 1、在不阻止習近平施行終身制的前提下，習確保江氏家族在政治和經濟上的永久安全。 2、江點名的那幾個親信必須進入政治局及常委會、人大、政協，習並且要保證這些人退休後安全落地。 3、江點名的黨內仇敵的後代，不再提拔。 4、不平反六四。 5、對法輪功的定性不變。"},{"pid":"e6a9dc44033d41838b479a728f946e3f21b0af58","tid":585703,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T01:54:09.000Z","msg":"愛支泛民 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3557092800edf98404f1d0cdd3b0371f92714c5b","tid":585703,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T01:56:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3bdca74bc5a85f5b626bb4ec455c595b036ab67","tid":585703,"uid":31637,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:44:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.aboluowang.com/2018/0303/1078577.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.aboluowang.com%2F2018%2F0303%2F1078577.html&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pvzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=cff4acd7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.aboluowang.com/2018/0303/1078577.html</a><br />\n<br />\n人民報獨家：習近平江澤民已達成協議<br />\n【阿波羅新聞網 2018-03-03 訊】作者：姜平默認<br />\n主要內容如下： 1、在不阻止習近平施行終身制的前提下，習確保江氏家族在政治和經濟上的永久安全。 2、江點名的那幾個親信必須進入政治局及常委會、人大、政協，習並且要保證這些人退休後安全落地。 3、江點名的黨內仇敵的後代，不再提拔。 4、不平反六四。 <span style=\"color: red;\">5、對法輪功的定性不變</span>。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抵撚死,奶習奶得咁撚爽"},{"pid":"4101e0642acd8222b186647c0f1f79c31a2b7d25","tid":585703,"uid":37735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:45:47.000Z","msg":"支聯會：好總理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819b53902c1b068164a7d46cc54c1e9e75f0f0a0","tid":585703,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T04:41:37.000Z","msg":"仇敵係楊家將仲有無其他?"},{"pid":"44d984e5e0104bfe566e887cec427d3a77ae536a","tid":585703,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T04:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愛支泛民 &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支那會：超好消費，$$$$$$，年年見！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b05ee9092ba25852bf6595d84253b6d2c3865c2","tid":585703,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T04:55:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愛支泛民 &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=